lead_paragraph: The most powerful executives in the banking industry did not go to the government.
snippet: The widely expected prospect of a Republican takeover of the House of Representatives and possibly the Senate would be warmly welcomed by the banks, who want a break from the regulatory push of the last two years.

headline.main: Financial Executives Expect Benefits From Midterm Elections
